      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for by its sole owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any stone chips or scratches. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. A buyer can expect a car that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
