      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous, uncompromising care. Every mechanical and aesthetic component functions with absolute precision, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection in both presentation and performance.",
