    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This is an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen retains its original factory finishes and exhibits zero track wear. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. All critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been documented and performed using OEM components. The chassis remains taut with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system functioning to factory specifications, while the carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof shows no UV degradation. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak BMW M-division engineering in a pristine, unmodified state.",
